        (1821480, 'Kahaani', 2012, 95510, 8, 122, 1200000, 16000000, 'Vidya Bagchi (Vidya Balan) arrives in Kolkata from London to find her missing husband Arnab Bagchi. Seven months pregnant and alone in a festive city, she begins a relentless search for her husband. With nothing to rely on except fragments from her memories about him, all clues seem to reach a dead end when everyone tries to convince Vidya that her husband does not exist. She slowly realises that nothing is what it seems. In a city soaked in lies, Vidya is determined to unravel the truth about her husband - for herself and her unborn child - even at the cost of her own life.', '/dlmlky00UXfAMzMPhajyLp5njHN.jpg', '/aTXRaPrWSinhcmCrcfJK17urp3F.jpg', 0),
