        (1828976, 'Good Luck Charlie, It''s Christmas!', 2011, 15042, 6, 182, 0, 0, 'Teddy Duncan''s middle-class family embarks on a road trip from their home in Denver to visit Mrs. Duncans Parents, the Blankenhoopers, in Palm Springs. When they find themselves stranded between Denver and Utah, they try to hitch a ride to Las Vegas with a seemingly normal older couple in a station wagon from Roswell, New Mexico. It turns out that the couple believes they are the victims of alien abduction. The Duncan''s must resort to purchasing a clunker Yugo to get to Utah, have their luggage stolen in Las Vegas, and survive a zany Christmas with Grandpa and Grandma Blankenhooper.', '/nnQrxzPtMqgAdgeyiinmXEppA0P.jpg', '/p3Lo5mBJgKIXdaX91sfXeCI9BqY.jpg', 0),
        (1830499, 'Beur sur la ville', 2011, 108060, 4, 59, 0, 0, '25-year-old Khalid Belkacem has failed at everything: college education, summer camp instructor''s permit, driver''s license, and even his BCG. He never expected to become the first "positive discrimination" member of the police force. But as his mother says: "That''s France for you! A country where everyone has a chance."', '/1gfgOh1sTOjT10AHLORzuyiCr4U.jpg', '/gM9yof03x3ZRdv0Gu0pXbnMtPl9.jpg', 0),
        (1830633, 'Home Makeover', 2010, 220833, 7, 89, 0, 0, 'The Minions have to make Gru''s home safe for the children, before Child Services arrive!', '/43TK5GtHUiPelQpnSX0bl9ONLh0.jpg', '/uRlT6hzUE6pMCtSsUhKd7OtjD1l.jpg', 0),
